{"tid":2055284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主社會vs極權統治社會","createTime":"2020-06-07T23:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T05:31:51.000Z","uid":268271,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb200dadff41990e67c084163f395ebe43aab64","tid":2055284,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:50:57.000Z","msg":"臺灣 vs 香港 : <br />\n1. 臺灣市民有選舉權, 可自由選擇總統、立法委員、市長<br />\n2. 臺灣市民有公投權, 可踢走垃圾市長, 香港人幾時可踢走個垃圾市長呢?<br />\n<br />\n美國vs 香港 : <br />\n1. 美國警察濫用暴力,  也會被告或辭退, 例如: 推示威者倒地, 拉下示威者口罩, etc<br />\n2. 同袍濫用暴力, 美國警察會公開道歉<br />\n3. 美國人可向法庭申請, 禁美國警察使用催淚彈及橡膠子彈對付示威者<br />\n4. 美國唔會因疫情, 禁止市民上街示威<br />\nvs 香港呢 ?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港重係民主社會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港已變為極權統治社會"},{"pid":"fb7d0efba7efe1b7f79ee6a65f7f2a40a6f7337e","tid":2055284,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"點解美國應對疫情會輸比中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f43c9e4383d9e4e4cb20bcafef21960d7b59252","tid":2055284,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb7d0efba7efe1b7f79ee6a65f7f2a40a6f7337e","tid":2055284,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"點解美國應對疫情會輸比中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"因為老共隱瞞真實數字囉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}